# Webapp sharing. Managed by the /app dashboard share toggles.
# Format: <sharer-slug>:<port> per line. Caddy never reads this file —
# /internal/check-shared on the portal answers Caddy via forward_auth
# when a request arrives at /shared/<sharer>/p/<port>/.
#
# Example (delete this file once the portal has written to it):
# justin.cronin:8080
# alice.smith:3000
